Victoire CMS {{ widget }} Bundle
============

Need to add a {{ widget|lower }} in a victoire cms website ?
Get this {{ widget|lower }} bundle and so on

First you need to have a valid Symfony2 Victoire edition.
Then you just have to run the following composer command :

    php composer.phar require victoire/{{ widget|lower }}-bundle

The {{ widget|lower }} bundle handles Bootstrap and Foundation view.


Do not forget to add the bundle in your AppKernel !

    class AppKernel extends Kernel
    {
        public function registerBundles()
        {
            $bundles = array(
                ...
                new {{ namespace }}\{{ bundle }}(),
            );

            return $bundles;
        }
    }

